{"type":"message","id":"bcb729b0","parentId":"30f52991","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:19:09.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a system message about an exec completion with an error in the media-crawler-mcp. Let me check the heartbeat file."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab841d7b935a442a899d3011","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783480743485}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae08f50b","parentId":"bcb729b0","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:19:09.553Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ab841d7b935a442a899d3011","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783480749551}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d76a4a8","parentId":"ae08f50b","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:19:14.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time is 11:19 (Asia/Shanghai) on Wednesday July 8th, 2026. This is within the 9:30-11:30 morning work window.\n\nLet me check the rules:\n1. 喝水提醒 at 10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 - it's 11:19, not near these times\n2. 久坐提醒 - I don't have context on whether user has been working continuously\n3. 周五 17:00 - It's Wednesday, not Friday\n\nSince it's 11:19, I'm in the work window but none of the specific triggers are hitting right now. \n\nNo active tasks in the workspace either, so I'll just respond with HEARTBEAT_OK"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783480749554}}
